{
  "name": "RPlog_Letting_the_Chips_Fall",
  "title": "Letting the Chips Fall",
  "summary": "Aboard his flagship Remittance, the Twi'lek crimelord Tyy'sun Eson receives his haggard lieutenant Gren Delede with grim news: the Empire has launched a program to purge the Maffi organization and is interrogating the captured Twila Virda, putting Governor Laran on their trail. The report ignites Eson's dark-side fury, and he seizes Delede by the throat in a rage while the timid Bith crewman Scrat cowers under a desk. Delede remains defiant, warning that these orders come straight from the Emperor himself, and Eson grudgingly admits respect for the lieutenant's nerve before releasing him. Delede pledges to begin investigating the threat at once, departing with a fresh wound and Eson's warning that betrayal would bring the wrath of the entire Family down upon him.",
